        "created_at": "2019-05-30T12:13:55.437Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi! I have five data centers with three instances in each DC, and I need to have the possibility to write/read data in/from each data center. So which replication method I should prefer?   Is three_datacenter method will fulfill my needs or I need to choose region configuration instead?</p>",
